---
// index.astro — Dossier (Data Core Hero, Deep Frost, Bulletproof Mobile)
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vedant // Dossier</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/@studio-freight/lenis@1.0.39/dist/lenis.min.js"></script>

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      /* Everforest Base Palette */
      --bg: #0d120a; 
      --bg-dark: #050704;
      --fg: #f4f4f0;
      --accent: #A7C080; 
      
      --font-massive: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }

    body {
      width: 100%;
      overflow-x: clip;
      overflow-y: auto;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      color: var(--fg);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      cursor: none; 
    }

    a, button { cursor: none; }

    html.lenis, html.lenis body { height: auto; }
    .lenis.lenis-smooth { scroll-behavior: auto !important; }
    .lenis.lenis-stopped { overflow: hidden; }

    /* ─── TACTICAL CROSSHAIR CURSOR ─── */
    #tactical-cursor { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 99999; mix-blend-mode: difference; }
    .cursor-dot { position: absolute; width: 4px; height: 4px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
    .cursor-ring { position: absolute; width: 30px; height: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.6); border-radius: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); transition: width 0.2s ease, height 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease; }
    .cursor-hover .cursor-ring { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.1); border-color: var(--accent); }

    /* ─── 1. LOADER ─── */
    #loader { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: var(--bg-dark); z-index: 100; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.8, 0, 0.2, 1); }
    .loader-text { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--fg); }
    .progress-track { width: 250px; height: 2px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .progress-fill { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100%; width: 0%; background: var(--accent); transition: width 0.1s linear; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent); }

    /* ─── 2. HERO SECTION (TACTICAL DATA CORE) ─── */
    .hero-container { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; z-index: 1; will-change: transform; background: var(--bg-dark); }
    .bg-parallax-wrapper { position: absolute; inset: -50px; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .css-bg-container { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; will-change: transform; transition: transform 0.1s ease-out; }

    /* Massive Breathing Core Glows */
    .ambient-glow { position: absolute; width: 80vw; height: 80vh; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.25) 0%, transparent 65%); top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(80px); z-index: 1; animation: pulseGlow 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate; }
    .ambient-glow.top-left { top: 0%; left: 10%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%); width: 60vw; height: 60vw; animation-delay: -2s; animation-duration: 12s; }
    .ambient-glow.bottom-right { top: 100%; left: 90%; width: 70vw; height: 70vw; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%); animation-delay: -5s; animation-duration: 10s; }
    
    @keyframes pulseGlow { 0% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8); } 100% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.3); } }

    /* Tactical Architecture Grid */
    .css-grid-lines {
      position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 2;
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 50px 50px; background-position: center center;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 30%, transparent 80%);
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 30%, transparent 80%);
    }

    .content-wrapper { position: relative; z-index: 10; padding: 0 5vw; margin-top: -5vh; pointer-events: none; will-change: opacity; }
    .name-container { pointer-events: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 90vw; margin: 0 auto; cursor: none; }
    .first-name, .last-name { font-family: var(--font-massive); font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(3rem, 11vw, 11.5rem); line-height: 0.85; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: -0.03em; white-space: nowrap; }
    .first-name { align-self: flex-start; color: var(--fg); transition: color 0.6s ease, letter-spacing 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1), text-shadow 0.6s ease; }
    .first-name:hover { color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.015em; text-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.4); }
    .last-name { align-self: flex-end; color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.8); transition: color 0.4s ease, -webkit-text-stroke 0.4s ease, transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275); }
    .last-name:hover { color: var(--fg); -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px transparent; transform: translateX(15px); text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); }
    
    .hero-desc { margin-top: 2rem; align-self: flex-end; margin-right: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.8); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .hero-desc::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 30px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }

    .ticker-wrap { position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 0; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; background: rgba(5,7,4,0.3); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); z-index: 20; border-top: 1px solid rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.15); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.15); padding: 1rem 0; display: flex; pointer-events: none; will-change: opacity; }
    .ticker { display: flex; white-space: nowrap; animation: ticker-loop 20s linear infinite; }
    .ticker-content { display: flex; flex-shrink: 0; padding-right: 2rem; }
    .ticker-item { padding: 0 2rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.6); }
    .ticker-item span { color: var(--accent); text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.4); }
    @keyframes ticker-loop { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } }

    /* ─── UNIVERSAL DEEP FROST GLASS CLASS ─── */
    .glass-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); 
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), inset 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    }

    /* ─── 3. ABOUT SECTION ─── */
    .about-section { position: relative; z-index: 10; margin-top: 100vh; width: 100vw; min-height: 120vh; 
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(23, 30, 20, 1) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 70%); 
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 15vh 5vw; overflow: hidden; }
    .about-section::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -15vh; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 15vh; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5,7,4,0) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 100%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
    .bg-watermark { position: absolute; top: -10vh; left: -2vw; font-family: var(--font-massive); font-size: 45vw; line-height: 0.8; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02); -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04); z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; will-change: transform; }

    .about-container { position: relative; z-index: 10; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8rem; width: 100%; max-width: 90vw; margin: 0 auto; }
    .about-top-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 5vw; }
    .manifesto-block { flex: 1.2; }
    .about-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 3rem; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.3); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.2); }
    .about-headline { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 3rem); line-height: 1.3; color: var(--fg); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .about-headline strong { font-family: var(--font-massive); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-top: 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }

    .asset-wrapper { flex: 0.8; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; position: relative; }
    .asset-card { width: clamp(280px, 25vw, 450px); aspect-ratio: 3/4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; will-change: transform; }
    .asset-card::before, .asset-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; width: 15px; height: 15px; border: 1px solid var(--accent); opacity: 0.5; }
    .asset-card::before { top: -1px; left: -1px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
    .asset-card::after { bottom: -1px; right: -1px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }
    .asset-placeholder-text { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; }
    
    .rotating-badge { position: absolute; bottom: -3rem; left: -3rem; width: 120px; height: 120px; animation: spin 12s linear infinite; z-index: 20; }
    @keyframes spin { 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .about-modules { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); padding-top: 3rem; }
    .module-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; padding: 2.5rem; transition: border-color 0.4s ease, background 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease; }
    .module-card:hover { border-color: rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.4); background: rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.03); transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 30px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), inset 0 0 20px rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.05); }
    .module-header { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #fff; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .module-header span:last-child { color: var(--accent); }
    .module-text { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.7); }

    /* ─── 4. PROJECTS GALLERY (DEEP FROST ENCASED) ─── */
    .projects-section { position: relative; z-index: 10; width: 100vw; 
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(23, 30, 20, 0.8) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 60%); 
      padding: 15vh 5vw 25vh 5vw; }
    .projects-header { width: 100%; max-width: 90vw; margin: 0 auto 10vh auto; text-align: right; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); padding-bottom: 2rem; }
    .projects-title { font-family: var(--font-massive); font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem); font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    
    .projects-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4vw; width: 100%; max-width: 90vw; margin: 0 auto; align-items: flex-start; }
    .grid-column { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4vw; }
    .grid-column.right { margin-top: 15vh; will-change: transform; }

    .project-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; position: relative; padding: 1.5rem; transition: transform 0.4s ease, border-color 0.4s ease; }
    .project-card:hover { border-color: rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.4); transform: translateY(-5px); }
    
    .project-image-container { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3; overflow: hidden; position: relative; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
    .project-image { width: 100%; height: 100%; transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .project-card:hover .project-image { transform: scale(1.03); }
    
    .project-image-container::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -100%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 20%; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(167, 192, 128, 0.3), transparent); z-index: 5; pointer-events: none; transition: top 0.1s; }
    .project-card:hover .project-image-container::after { animation: scanSweep 2s linear infinite; }
    @keyframes scanSweep { 0% { top: -20%; } 100% { top: 120%; } }

    .project-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; padding-left: 0.5rem; border-left: 2px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.3s ease; }
    .project-card:hover .project-meta { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
    .project-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .project-name { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--fg); letter-spacing: -0.01em; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
    .project-card:hover .project-name { color: #fff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

    /* ─── 5. CONTACT / HANDSHAKE SECTION ─── */
    .contact-section { position: relative; z-index: 10; width: 100vw; 
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 90%, rgba(23, 30, 20, 0.8) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 70%); 
      padding: 10vh 5vw 5vh 5vw; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    
    .contact-container { width: 100%; max-width: 90vw; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10vh; }
    .contact-header { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .contact-headline { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem); font-weight: 300; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .contact-links-wrapper { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2rem; }
    .magnetic-wrap { display: inline-block; padding: 2rem; margin: -2rem; }
    
    /* Safely clamped down so 18 characters perfectly fit the screen */
    .magnetic-text { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-massive); font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 4.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--fg); text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 0.9; word-break: break-word; transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275); will-change: transform; }
    
    .social-row { display: flex; gap: 4vw; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .social-text { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem); color: rgba(244, 244, 240, 0.6); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
    .social-text:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-top: 2rem; margin-top: 10vh; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: rgba(244,244,240,0.4); text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* Scroll Reveal */
    .reveal-elem { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: opacity 1s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1), transform 1s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1); }
    .reveal-elem.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* ─── GLOBAL MOBILE LOCK (PERFECTED) ─── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        body, html { overflow-x: clip !important; cursor: auto !important; }
        a, button { cursor: auto !important; }
        #tactical-cursor { display: none !important; }

        .name-container { margin: 0; align-items: flex-start; max-width: 100%; }
        .first-name, .last-name { font-size: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 3.5rem) !important; align-self: flex-start !important; }
        .last-name { margin-left: 1rem !important; }
        .hero-desc { align-self: flex-start !important; margin-right: 0 !important; margin-left: 1rem !important; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; text-align: left; max-width: 85vw; }
        .hero-desc::before { display: none; }

        .about-section { padding: 10vh 5vw; }
        .bg-watermark { font-size: 80vw; top: 0; left: -5vw; }
        .about-top-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 3rem; }
        .about-headline { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 2rem) !important; } 
        .asset-wrapper { width: 100%; justify-content: flex-start; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .about-modules { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }

        .projects-header { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 5vh; }
        .projects-title { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 7.5vw, 3rem) !important; line-height: 1.1 !important; letter-spacing: -0.04em !important; word-wrap: normal !important; overflow-wrap: normal !important; }
        .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 6vh; }
        .grid-column.right { margin-top: 0; transform: none !important; }

        .contact-headline { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 8vw, 2.5rem) !important; }
        .magnetic-text { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 3rem) !important; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1; }
        .social-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .social-text { font-size: 1rem !important; }
        .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; margin-top: 6vh; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div id="tactical-cursor">
    <div class="cursor-dot"></div>
    <div class="cursor-ring" id="cursor-ring"></div>
  </div>

  <div id="loader">
    <div class="loader-text">Initializing Systems</div>
    <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div></div>
  </div>

  <main class="hero-container" id="hero">
    <div class="bg-parallax-wrapper">
      <div id="bg-parallax" class="css-bg-container">
        <div class="ambient-glow"></div>
        <div class="ambient-glow top-left"></div>
        <div class="ambient-glow bottom-right"></div>
        <div class="css-grid-lines"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content-wrapper" id="hero-content">
      <div class="name-container">
        <span class="first-name">Vedant</span>
        <span class="last-name">Cholkar</span>
        <div class="hero-desc">System Architecture // Web Reconnaissance</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ticker-wrap" id="hero-ticker">
      <div class="ticker">
        <div class="ticker-content">
          <div class="ticker-item">SYS: <span>FEDORA</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">STATUS: <span>ACTIVE RECON</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">ACOUSTIC DYNAMICS</div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">DEST: <span>TOKYO 2026</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">INITIATING AADVIK_TEKLABS</div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ticker-content">
          <div class="ticker-item">SYS: <span>FEDORA</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">STATUS: <span>ACTIVE RECON</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">ACOUSTIC DYNAMICS</div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">DEST: <span>TOKYO 2026</span></div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
          <div class="ticker-item">INITIATING AADVIK_TEKLABS</div><div class="ticker-item">///</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <section class="about-section" id="about">
    <div class="bg-watermark" id="scroll-watermark">01</div>
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="about-top-row">
        <div class="manifesto-block reveal-elem">
          <span class="about-label">IDENT // V.CHOLKAR</span>
          <h2 class="about-headline">
            Operating out of Bengaluru, driven by a singular baseline:
            <strong>Buy nice,<br>or buy twice.</strong>
            Optimization is not an afterthought; it is the foundation.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="asset-wrapper reveal-elem" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="asset-card glass-card" id="scroll-asset">
            <span class="asset-placeholder-text">[ VISUAL ASSET // PROFILE ]</span>
            <svg class="rotating-badge" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,6" opacity="0.5"/>
              <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="35" fill="none" stroke="var(--fg)" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.3"/>
              <path d="M50 10 L50 20 M50 90 L50 80 M10 50 L20 50 M90 50 L80 50" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-modules">
        <div class="module-card glass-card reveal-elem" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="module-header"><span>[ Module_A ]</span><span>The Architecture</span></div>
          <p class="module-text">A dual discipline. The uncompromising structure of web application reconnaissance, mapping vulnerabilities and executing precise tooling, balanced against the raw physical tension and exact rhythm required for Spanish Flamenco acoustic performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="module-card glass-card reveal-elem" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="module-header"><span>[ Module_B ]</span><span>Current Trajectory</span></div>
          <p class="module-text">Executing hardware and system optimizations on Fedora Linux. Currently preparing for active operations at Aadvik Teklabs, alongside a calculated, multi-phase trajectory targeting engineering deployment in Japan via MEXT 2026.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

